n明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\nPrayer Meeting for Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy<br />\n<br />\nThe Letter of No Objection for the meeting (at Chater Garden) and the procession (to US Consulate) has been issued.<br />\n<br />\nThe Meeting<br />\nVenue: Chater Garden, Central<br />\nTime: 13:30-18:30<br />\nSubtheme for each session:<br />\n&quot;Chosen People&quot;, &quot;Praise in Prison&quot;, &quot;Judgement Shall Come&quot;,  &quot;God Bless America&quot;<br />\n<br />\n※※ Signatures for the Declaration of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy will be collected at Chater Garden until 14:30, then be submitted to US Consulate in the procession ※※<br />\n<br />\nThe Procession<br />\nAssemble Point: Chater Garden near Queensway<br />\nAssemble Time: 14:30<br />\nRoute: Start at Chater Garden, go along Garden Road and submit petition letter to US Consulate General at public activity area near bus stop at Lower Albert Road<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dEdZcy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dEdZcy.jpg&h=9d27a5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjKYqSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjKYqSz.jpg&h=ba976118&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0f2481e19b3bcef9149afcf2c726c65180cc18c","tid":1549081,"uid":28951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCxSvgD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCxSvgD.png&h=c73ab974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[認真]  既然要國際支援，點解唔講出嚟？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546622</a><br />\n- 分享