s,<br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched,<br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare,<br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\nGave proof through the night,<br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\nOh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave."},{"pid":"2e3941258d8904ecbe1477661e243913bb164e49","tid":1549081,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686ea8dd350fd8008e5e0ed794d5962af3d15b3c","tid":1549081,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235a3ff0427c75120d3bc81708a81dcd05328909","tid":1549081,"uid":277540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:39:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/香港勇武前線基金/?fbclid=IwAR2HKWTYAPTXK7ZBXRz2fwwJD8mhOMCOso9sN48hc6UvdSrcpvQWYOvpNX8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2HKWTYAPTXK7ZBXRz2fwwJD8mhOMCOso9sN48hc6UvdSrcpvQWYOvpNX8&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=9b6b52fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/香港勇武前線基金/?fbclid=IwAR2HKWTYAPTXK7ZBXRz2fwwJD8mhOMCOso9sN48hc6UvdSrcpvQWYOvpNX8</a>"},{"pid":"39587b9908d8734bd88d99cfee3d04451d880697","tid":1549081,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"[警世][最終文宣] 喚醒對中共既不信任 聯合世界圍堵#Chinazi<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c